text:
Located just along Ang Mo Kio Ave 1 near junction of AMK Ave 10.The Depot is situated inbetween Ang Mo Kio HDB Estate and Bishan HDB Estate.It can hold quite a substancial number of mrt trains when they are off service.It also acts as a repair and servicing centre for the mrt trains.

Dated : 07/08/2018 ( Tuesday ).
Beside orderly, serves as depot for the MRT system. Friendly fast cosy ambience with safety professional advanced facilities efficiently & smoothly run..
Best transport way in singapore.well aranged
